Major update
1. Course update. Added 6，7，8，9 four new stage;
2. Reward updates. Cancellation of admission fees allows experienced players to experience more advanced gameplay, as well as more gold coins and treasure chest rewards for you;
3. Invite friends. Added the Invite Friends Battle feature, then you can play online with your Facebook friends and compare your skills.
4, optimized the batting effects and tailing effects, increased the game prompt sound
5, fixed a few bugs that affect the experience

1.Brand new “Kingdom” mode! Kingdom is a month long event where you can compete against real players from all over the world in 1v1 matches to obtain points and win HUGE prizes!
2.New Arena offers will be available in the store while the Arena is open.
3.Players can create new guest accounts and switch between accounts.
4.We’ve improved the UI with new visual effects!

*Follow us page “Golf Rival” on Facebook for more information about the Kingdom!
